{"descriptions":[{"id":1330,"title":null,"content":"\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThis suffix is used to ask quantitative questions like \u0026ldquo;How big?\u0026rdquo; \u0026ldquo;How heavy?\u0026rdquo; and so forth. It is placed directly after the short form of the adjective:\u003c/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eལྗི་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Heavy,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eལྗི་ལོས་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;How heavy?\u0026rdquo; \u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཆེན་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Big,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཆེ་ལོས་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;How big?\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཐག་རིང་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Far,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཐག་རིང་ལོས་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;How far?\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e \u003c/ul\u003e","source_url":null,"is_primary":true,"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:39 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:39 UTC","authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}]}]}